nodes.text: The KL-1F was a landspeeder model produced by Korrealis Systems during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire.
The Korrealis KL-1F was first added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic on October 20, 2015 as one of the items in the Underworld Alliance Pack on the Cartel Market.
